casebody.data:
No. 33,

Mise.

Odom v. United States.

C. A. 5th Cir. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted, limited to retroactivity of North Carolina v. Pearce, 395 U. S. 711, and case transferred to appellate docket.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and petition.
